description:
China is a first year student at the middle school section of the Seifuu Private Academy, class president, and member of the art club. Her home is the restaurant Kousaka. As she watches http://anidb.net/ch57667 [Sei] get interested in Gundam plastic model battles, she herself becomes intrigued with the sport. She has a wise and reserved personality. Her chest is also "reserved."
Source: ANN
name: Kousaka China
